data.title: American Legal Publishing
data.meta_description: Legal publisher offering ordinance codification services for local governments, specializing in providing codes of ordinances in print and on the Internet
data.text: *There may be discrepancies in the code when translating to other languages. Please note that the English language version is the official version of the code. American Legal Publishing and the jurisdiction whose laws are being translated do not vouch for the accuracy of any translated versions of such laws. PDF documents are not translated.
